```
Raw pickle (residue_wise.pkl)
  → 00_precompute_tokens_and_labels.py  →  tokens_*.pt
  → 01_split_datasets.py               →  split_*.pt  (indices only)
  → 02_run_training.py or scripts/frameworks/*.py  (loads both files)
```

